Xaaladaha si dhakhso leh u beddelaya, qiyaasta ugu dambeysa ee cudurka faafa iyo culeyska ayaa la go'aami doonaa in la gaaro.
Daraasad xarumo badan oo la sameeyay Febraayo 11, 2020, ayaa lagu sameeyay 8,866 bukaan oo ay ku jiraan 4,021 bukaan oo COVID-19 ah oo la xaqiijiyay oo muujinaya xaaladda ugu dambeysa ee cudurka faafa (https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/UlBi-HX_rHPXa1qHA2bhdA).
SARS-CoV-2 waxay ku dhacdaa da 'kasta, laakiin waxay inta badan ku dhacdaa dadka da'doodu u dhaxayso 30-65 sano.
Qiyaastii kala bar dadka qaba fayraska (47.7%) waa in ka badan 50 sano, tiro yar oo ka yar 20 sano, 14 qof oo kaliya ayaa ka yar 10 sano.
Tirada ragga qaba SARS-CoV-2 (0.31/100,000) ayaa ka badan dumarka (0.27/100,000).
COVID-19 ayaa inta badan ku faafay Xubey iyo agagaarkeeda.
Waxay qaadataa celcelis ahaan 5 (2-9) maalmood in baaritaanka lagu ogaado laga bilaabo taariikhda la qabtay COVID-19.
Calaamadaha cudurka ayaa bilaabanaya celcelis ahaan 4.8 (3.0-7.2) maalmood.
Celceliska muddada uu ku noolaado cudurka ayaa ahaa 9.5 (4.8-13).
Tirada dhalashada aasaasiga ah (R0) waxay ahayd 3.77 (95% CI: 3.51-4.05) halka R0 la hagaajinayo ay ahayd 2.23-4.82.
Tirada dadka qaba fayraska ayaa si weyn u kordhay ka hor Janaayo 23/2020, oo ah waqtiga gaadiidka ee xidhiidhka leh Bandhigga Gu'ga ee Shiinaha.
Tirada dhimashada ee bukaannada qaba kiisaska la xaqiijiyay waxay ahayd 1.44% (95% CI: 1.10-1.86%) iyo heerka dhimashada ee la hagaajinayo ee dhammaan bukaannada wuxuu ahaa 3.06% (95% CI: 2.02-4.59%).
Saddexda arrimood ee ugu muhiimsan ee halista ah ee COVID-19 waxay ahaayeen jinsiga (nin), da'da (≥60) iyo cudurka qanjirka 'scab' ee daran.
CoVs waa qoys yar oo ka mid ah fayrasyada ballaaran ee isku xirta oo leh hal fasal RNA.
Waxaa loo qaybin karaa afar qaybood oo guud: alfa, beta, gamma iyo delta, oo laga ogaado in alfa iyo beta CoVs ay dadka ku dhacaan.
Envelope Spike (S) glycoprotein wuxuu ku xiran yahay SARS-CoV iyo MERS-CoV oo ka soo jeeda enzymes-ka beddelaya angiotensin receptor 2 (ACE2) iyo diptidyl peptidase 4 (DPP4) ka dibna waxaa la sameeyaa isku-darka unugyada.
Jenooyinka RNA ee fayraska ayaa loo sii daayaa sitoplasma; ka dib markii ay u baahdaan genome fayraska, RNA-ga iyo borotiinka envelopes waxay sameeyaan jirka gudaha ama dibadda ee fayraska leh, oo leh glycoproteins iyo nucleocapside proteins, taas oo ka dhigeysa fayraska inuu ku xirmo unugyada plasma.
Sawirka ugu horreeya ee SARS-CoV-2 ayaa la soo sheegay 10ka Janaayo, 2020.
Marka SARS-CoV-2 la ogaado inay tahay nooc cusub oo beta-CoV ah, waxaa laga helay in ka badan 99.98% isku midnimada jinsiga ah oo ka mid ah 10 shaybaar oo laga soo qaaday suuqa cuntada badda ee Hunan ee biyaha uu masiibadu ka bilowday.
SARS-CoV-2 waxay u egtahay SARS-CoV halkii ay u egtahay MERS-CoV.
Iyada oo loo marayo microscopy electron transmission, waxyaabaha yaryar ee SARS-CoV-2 ayaa laga helay qaybaha ugu khafiifsan ee neefsashada aadanaha.
Dadka ACE2 ayaa loo ogaaday inay tahay soo dhaweeysa SARS-CoV-2 iyo SARS-CoV.
Si kastaba ha noqotee, isku xirnaanta borotiinka S ee SARS-CoV-2 ee aadanaha ee ACE2 ayaa ka yar SARS-CoV, taas oo ka dhigeysa in cudurka SARS-CoV-2 uu ka yar yahay cudurka daran ee SARS-CoV ee dadka buka.
SARS-CoV-2 waa borotiinka gaaban ee loo yaqaan 'novel short protein' oo loo sameeyay sirta orf3b loona sii daayo difaaca borotiinka orf8.
Fayraska SARS-CoV-2 orf3b wuxuu door ka qaadan karaa habka loo soo saaro cudurka wuxuuna xakameyn karaa muujinta IFNβ, si kastaba ha noqotee, orf8 ma laha wax domain ama kicin la yaqaan.
Bishii Febraayo 18/2020, Zhu iyo asxaabtiisu waxay soo sheegeen in dhererka buuxa ee ACE2 ee bini'aadamka uu yahay qaab dhismeedka Crio EM 2.9 Å, oo ka soo jeeda isku darka xamuulka amino acid B0AT1.
Caddaynta furan iyo xiran ayaa xaqiijisay in isku-darka dib-u-dhiska ah ee sida diamer ah loo sameeyay iyo in isku-darka ACE2-B0AT1 uu isku xirayo laba borotiinka S, taas oo ah caddaynta aqoonsiga iyo cudurka CoV.
B0AT1 waxay noqon kartaa bartilmaameedka daaweynta daawada ee lagu daaweeyo cudurka SARS-CoV-2.
