Bishii Maarso 19-2020 FDA waxay oggolaatay isticmaalka xaaladaha degdegga ah (EUA) ee Abbott Laboratories, oo tijaabinaya nidaamka Abbott m2000, iyadoo FDA ay oggolaansho la mid ah siisay Hologic, LabCorp iyo Thermo Fisher Scientific.
