Xakamaynta khatarta goobta shaqada ee COVID-19
Xakamaynta khatarta goobta shaqada ee COVID-19 waxay ka dhigeysaa nidaamyada badbaadada goobta shaqada inay ka hortagaan xakamaynta cudurka coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19).
Xakamaynta khatarta ee saxda ah ee goobta shaqada waxay ku saleysan tahay goobta shaqada iyo nooca shaqada, iyadoo lagu ogaanayo halista halista ilaha halista ah, baahinta bulshada iyo xaaladaha halista ah ee COVID-19 ee shaqsigu.
Sida laga soo xigtay Maamulka Badbaadada iyo Caafimaadka Shaqada ee Mareykanka (OSHA), shaqooyinka khatarta hooseeya waa shaqooyin aan la xiriirin bulshada iyo asxaabta, taas oo loo baahan yahay tallaabooyin ka hortag ah oo ka hortagga cudurrada sida gacmaha maydho, shaqaalaha guriga ku haynta haddii ay jiran yihiin, nidaamka neefsashada iyo ka saarista nadaafadda iyo cudurrada caadiga ah.
Shaqooyinka halista u dhexeeya waa dadka si toos ah ula shaqeeya dadka aan la aqoon ama loo maleynayo inay haystaan COVID-19 laakiin ay la shaqeeyaan dadka laga yaabo inay ku caabudaan cudurka ka soo baxa ama safarada caalamiga ah ee joogtada ah.
Tani waxay ka kooban tahay dadka ka soo jeeda bulshada, sida dadka iskuulka, dadka ku nool meelaha ugu badan iyo kuwa ka soo jeeda meelaha tafaariiqda ee ugu sarreeya.
Kooxda xakamaynta khatarta, marka loo eego tallaabooyinka aasaasiga ah ee ka hortagga infekshanka, waa inay lahaataa qalab lagu ilaaliyo nabadgelyada iyo badbaadada shakhsiyeed oo adeegsanaya shaandhaynta hawada oo leh awood sare oo lagu shaandhayn karo, haddii qof qaba COVID-19.
OSHA waxay u aragtaa khatarta halista ah ee halista ah ee qof la yaqaan ama la tuhmayo COVID-19 inuu yahay mid aad u nugul, haddii shaqaalaha ay soo ururiyaan muunado laga helo dadka la yaqaan ama la tuhmayo inay qabaan COVID-19 marka ay wadaan hawo-soo-saarka hawada, waxay kordhin doontaa halista aadka u weyn.
Xakamaynta khatarta ee ku habboon shaqaalahaas waxaa ka mid ah xakamaynta injineernimada, sida neefsashada cadaadiska xun ee EFL iyo qalabka difaaca shaqsiyeed ee ku habboon shaqada.
Cudurka faafa ee COVID-19 wuxuu saameyn badan ku yeelan karaa goobta shaqada.
