b'Angiotensin - Enzyme-converting enzyme 2 (ACE2) waa enzyme ku jirta unugyada, qanjidhada dhiigga, wadnaha, kelyaha iyo qanjidhada unugyada (cellular membrane).
ACE2 waxay bartilmaameed u tahay daawo rajo leh daaweynta cudurrada xididdada dhiigga iyadoo hoos u dhigaya heerarka angolistin-II iyo kordhinta Ang (1-7) iyadoo la horjeedo dhaqdhaqaaqa enzyme-ka beddelaya angolistin (ACE). ACE2 waxay u adeegtaa inay noqoto barta gelitaanka unugyada qaar ka mid ah coronavirus.
Enzyme-ka aadanaha waxaa badanaa loo yaqaan hACE2.
Angrostein-enzyme 2 waa zinc oo ka kooban ironloenzyme oo ku yaal dusha sare ee unugyada endothelial iyo kuwa kale.
Protein-ka ACE2 wuxuu u qoondeysan yahay domain-ka N-terminal peptidase M2 iyo domain-ka C-terminal collectrin renal amino acid.
ACE2 waa nooc ka mid ah noocyada ugu badan ee cudurka faafa ee nooca I, oo ku yaal dusha sare ee saliidaha iyo qaybaha kale ee jirka, iyada oo enzyme-ku uu leeyahay aag firfircoon.
ACE2 waxaa laga gooyaa unugyada gudaha ee unugyada gudaha ee unugyada kale ee shadas, waxaana natiijadu u soo baxdaa dhiigga oo loo sii daayo borotiinka dhalaalaya, ugu dambeyntiina wuxuu u soo baxayaa cirbadaha.
ACE2 waxaa laga helaa inta badan xubnaha jirka: ACE2 waxaa ugu horreyn ku xiran unugyada unugyada nooca II ee unugyada sanbabada, unugyada yaryar ee mindhicirka, dhiigga iyo dhiigga, iyo xididdada dhiigga ee unugyada muruqyada jilicsan ee unugyada badankood.
ACE2 mRNA waxaa lagu qeexaa qalfoofka cerebral, striatrum, hypothalamus iyo unugyada maskaxda.
Shaqada ugu weyn ee ACE2 waa inay noqoto dheelitirka la xiriira ACE.
ACE angiotensin I waxay u wareejineysaa hormoonka angiotensin II ee vasoconstricting.
ACE2 waxay sidoo kale gooysaa foontada ku jirta anxiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) oo ah amino acid ah oo ah carboxylic terminal phenylalanine waxayna u beddeleysaa angiotestin (1-7), oo ah vasodilator (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
ACE2 waxay burburin kartaa [des-Arg9]-bradykinin, apelin, neurotensin, dynorphin A iyo ghrelin oo ay ku jiraan noocyo kale oo badan oo peptide ah.
ACE2 waxay sidoo kale xakameysaa xajmiga SLC6A19, oo ah qaadaha amino acid ee dhexdhexaad ah, waxaana la ogaaday inay ku lug leedahay cudurka Hartnap.
Sida borotiinka loo yaqaan 'transmembrane protein', ACE2 waxay u adeegtaa inay noqoto barta ugu weyn ee loo galo unugyada fayraska qaarkood ee corona, oo ay ku jiraan HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (virus-ka keena SARS); iyo SARS-CoV-2 (virus-ka keena COVID-19).
Gaar ahaan, borotiinka S1 ee SARS-CoV iyo SARS-CoV2 waxay ku xirmaan unugyada ACE2 enzyme domain waxayna u horseedaan in fayraska iyo enzymes-ka ay ku dhacaan iyo u gudbiyaan unugyada gudaha ee unugyada.
Nidaamkan gelitaanka wuxuu u baahan yahay in lagu sameeyo baaritaan hore oo ku saabsan borotiinka S ee TMPRSS2 ee martigeliyaha, taas oo ah dawada hadda lagu kalsoonaan karo. Tani waxay keentay in qaar ay u maleynayaan inay ka caawin karto la dagaalanka caabuqa iyadoo la yareynayo heerarka ACE2 ee unugyada.
Si kastaba ha noqotee, bulshooyinka xirfadeed iyo hay'adaha xakamaynta badankood waxay kugula talinayaan inay sii wadaan daaweynta caadiga ah ee ACE inhibitor iyo ARB.
A.E. ayaa lagu daabacay July 11, 2012, dib u eegis istiraatiiji ah iyo falanqayn meta-galineed oo lagu soo bandhigay in isticmaalka ACE inhibitors ay u muuqato in ay hoos u dhac ku dhacday cudurka sanbabada 34% marka la barbar dhigo xakamaynta.
Sidoo kale, fursadaha cudurka 'pneumonia' waxay la mid ahaayeen bukaannada la daaweeyey ee qaba hargabka 'ACE' ee halista ugu weyn ee cudurka 'pneumonia', gaar ahaan kuwa qaba maskaxda iyo wadnaha.
Adeegsiga ACE-da ayaa sidoo kale loo isticmaalay dhimashada la xiriirta cudurka 'pneumonia', natiijooyinkeeduna waxay ahaayeen kuwo ka hooseeya khatarta guud ee cudurka 'pneumonia'.
Unugyada ACE2 (rhACE2) ee aadanaha ayaa la rumeysan yahay inay yihiin daaweyn cusub oo loogu talagalay cudurka qanjirka 'acne' ee degdegga ah, oo ah cudurka neefsashada ee loo yaqaan 'lipossaccharide respiratory disorder' oo hagaajinaya dhiig-baxa iyo oksijiinta ilkaha doofaarka ee digaagga.
Nolosha nuska ah ee rhACE2 ee aadanaha waa qiyaastii 10 saacadood, bilowga ficilkeeduna waa 30 daqiiqo marka lagu daro 24 saacadood oo waxqabad (waqtiga).
Cilmi-baarayaal badan ayaa soo jeedinaya in rhACE2 uu noqon karo daawo rajo leh oo loogu talagalay cudurrada leh xakameeyayaasha nidaamka renin-angiotensin (RAS inhibitors) ee caadiga ah ama heerarka angiotensin II ee la faafiyo.
