Agaasimaha guud ee Ururka Caafimaadka Adduunka, Theodore Adhanom Gbagbolah ayaa sheegay in kaarboonka loo yaqaan 'corona', uu yahay fayraska markii ugu horreysay ee lagu ogaado inuu yahay fayraska, cudurka iyo 19 qof oo cudurka ku dhacay: Diseembar 31/2019.
